** Name:     USP_KCo_BeneVendorList      
** Short Desc:  Fetch All Bene Vendor List   
**      
** Full Description      
**        Get Bene Vendor List In Report Module      
**      
** Sample Call       
**      USP_KCo_BeneVendorList 'Beneficiary Payment', '<BeneVendorList>  
												  <List ID="588939" />
												  <List ID="606910" />
												  <List ID="610006" />
												 </BeneVendorList>'
